Class Summary
FamilyTestApp Class that runs a query family test, as generated by QueryGenApp and filled-in by test writers.
QGraphQueryTester runs all transformation paths, test that they produce same result and compares actual result to expected results
QueryDataPair Helper class used by FamilyTestApp to represent a query instance file and its associated data match file.
QueryGen The actual class that generates a set of qgraph2 query (xml) files from a (xml) specification.
QueryGenApp Application that generates a set of qgraph2 query (xml) files from a (xml) file.
QueryResultsValidator Helps compare expected and actual temporary SGI NSTs.
QueryTestFailure Simple class to store a test failure report
